graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller Manager]
        Controller -->|watches| DSPACR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPACR

    subgraph "DSP Stack (per DSPA)"
        APIServer[API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS+OAuth]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent]
        ScheduledWorkflow[Scheduled Workflow Controller]
        MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP]
        Minio[Minio<br/>9000/TCP S3 API]
        MLPUI[ML Pipelines UI<br/>3000/TCP HTTP<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS+OAuth]

        subgraph "MLMD Components (optional)"
            MLMDEnvoy[MLMD Envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC]
            MLMDgRPC[MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC]
            MLMDWriter[MLMD Writer]
        end

        APIServer -->|reads/writes| MariaDB
        APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
        PersistenceAgent -->|syncs metadata| APIServer
        PersistenceAgent -->|writes to| MariaDB
        ScheduledWorkflow -->|triggers runs| APIServer
        MLPUI -->|API calls| APIServer

        MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies| MLMDgRPC
        MLMDgRPC -->|reads/writes| MariaDB
        MLMDWriter -->|metadata| MLMDgRPC
    end

    Controller -->|creates/manages| APIServer
    Controller -->|creates/manages| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|creates/manages| ScheduledWorkflow
    Controller -->|creates/manages| MariaDB
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Minio
    Controller -->|creates/manages| MLPUI
    Controller -->|creates/manages| MLMDEnvoy

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy]
        ExternalS3[External S3 Storage<br/>AWS/Azure/etc]
        ExternalDB[External Database<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL]
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring]
    end

    APIServer -->|creates| Tekton
    PersistenceAgent -->|watches| Tekton
    APIServer -.->|production| ExternalS3
    APIServer -.->|production| ExternalDB
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates| APIServer
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates| MLPUI
    Dashboard -->|integrates| APIServer
    Controller -->|metrics| Monitoring

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSPACR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style APIServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PersistenceAgent fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ScheduledWorkflow fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MariaDB fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Minio fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Tekton fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ExternalS3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ExternalDB fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
